SECOND REGULAR SESSION
SENATE BILL NO. 1518
103RD GENERA L ASSEMBLY
INTRODUCED BY SENATOR SCHNELTING.
6430S.01I KRISTINA MARTIN, Secretary
AN ACT
To repeal section 650.240, RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof one new section relating to boiler
inspector qualifications.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section A. Section 650.240, RSMo, is repealed and one new
2 section enacted in lieu thereof, to be known as section 650.240,
3 to read as follows:
1 650.240. The director shall employ deputy inspectors
2 who shall be responsible to the chief inspector[ and who
3 shall have had at the time of appointment not less than five
4 years' experience in the construction, installation,
5 inspection, operation, maintenance, or repair of high
6 pressure boilers and pressure vessels as a mechanical
7 engineer, steam operating engineer, boilermaker, or boiler
8 inspector, and who shall have passed the examination
9 provided for in section 650.250].
